flowchart TD
    A["Lead creates task<br/>template: 'By doing this,<br/>I will achieve ...'"] --> B["Assign to member(s)<br/>due day + priority<br/>push notification"]
    R["Recurring task template<br/>daily / weekly / monthly / custom"] --> B
    B --> C["Todo"]
    C --> D["In Progress<br/>photos, checklist, comments<br/>(every comment must tag someone)"]
    D --> BL["Blocked<br/>lead notified"]
    BL --> D
    D --> E["Marked Done by assignee<br/>counts toward progress %<br/>immediately"]
    E --> P["Pending Verification"]
    P --> T{{"Tuesday meeting:<br/>verification team reviews"}}
    T --> SC["Assessment score 1–10 each:<br/>1. Necessity<br/>2. Effectiveness<br/>3. Hygiene & Beauty"]
    SC --> Q{"Verdict"}
    Q -->|"Done<br/>post verification"| DN["Task closes<br/>stays counted<br/>score joins person + vertical<br/>quality-of-work record"]
    Q -->|"Redo"| RD["Returns with comments<br/>progress rolled back"]
    RD --> C
    R -.->|"previous instance unfinished<br/>when next spawns"| ES["Stays open AND<br/>escalates to Lead"]
